r />\n<br />\n所以我認為佢唔好再做 爆料者<br />\n直接轉型做 海外革命領袖......一直宣傳革命, 一直用錢 建立黑水傭兵"},{"pid":"66b6179ce09f885c5a0f27f8e5ececd931b1922c","tid":2074871,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:40:23.000Z","msg":"每年都有好多 大陸商人 帶住資金逃亡去美國<br />\n但通常呢D 商人 去到美國, 就會安份守己, 過埋下半世, 唔好搞咁多野<br />\n<br />\n只有郭文貴 逃亡左去美國, 仲肯出錢出力 對抗中共<br />\n所以 連登仔 真係唔好成日笑郭文貴<br />\n<br />\n如果你地 是郭文貴,  帶住資金 逃亡左去美國之後<br />\n可能你地只會 日日飲紅酒, 屌鬼妹, 仲邊得閒對抗中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1fd3280eedc48c5117dbeeb35341073d4d6c66","tid":2074871,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"先唔理佢目的 行動力如何<br />\n但大家都有共同目的都係中共<br />\n即使大家聯合打唔贏<br />\n起碼都有個盟友（當然要定期檢視）"},{"pid":"471666d2def74e6a0652b3dac8200162779e9617","tid":2074871,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f87598baae7957c121b32a288279ab5e677e76e","tid":2074871,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"75a72f4f51c0cfefd5c0ca5f6b84bd17fec9b98a","tid":2074871,"uid":343754,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"你條柒頭都未跳樓死啦<br />\n講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"佢就算唔跳樓, 都應該裸泳找下數....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59a6ebcda53e01c5221aa48e256c38d461d630e","tid":2074871,"uid